<p style=\"margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; text-align: justify;\">
	<span style=\"margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times; font-size: medium;\">Tờ khai xin thị thực Schengen</span></p>
<p style=\"margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; text-align: justify;\">
	<span style=\"margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times; font-size: medium;\">+&nbsp; Giấy tờ chứng minh mối quan hệ thương mại giữa hai c&ocirc;ng ty</span></p>
<p style=\"margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; text-align: justify;\">
