	<span style=\"margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;\">2.Hồ sơ xin visa&nbsp;<a href=\"http://mixtourist.com.vn/tour/with/Tour-du-lich-Chau-au-y---Thuy-Sy---Phap---Bi---Ha-Lan/190\" style=\"margin: 0px; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 255);\">du lịch Bỉ</a></strong></span></p>
